data.description: Welcome home to this well maintained 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 1,881+/- sq ft. (BCAD) home located in Hunters Crossing.  This 3 sided brick home features updated Anderson Windows, an open floor plan, a large kitchen area, and more. Easily host family and friends with access to your great sized backyard from your kitchen, bring on the summer fun! Hunters Crossing offers a community pool, park, ponds, walking trails and much more. Located just minutes to necessary amenities, 4 miles to Downtown Bastrop where local shops and restaurants await , and only 21 miles to ABIA and Tesla, puts this home in a great location!
